0full-time%20jobs%20and%20don't%20want%20the%20hassle%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-airbnb-made-60000-three-years-2015-07%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanaging%20an%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20weekend%20or%20hiring%20a%20property%20manager.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20long-term%20rentals%20were%20better%20suited%20for%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlynn%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20Stefan%20and%20I%20still%20live%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20Long%20Island%2C%20Scott%20is%20temporarily%20living%20in%20the%20house.%20He%20got%20married%20in%202024%2C%20and%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20paying%20rent%20as%20they%20wait%20to%20buy%20their%20own%20home.%20After%20they%20move%20out%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20manage%20and%20rent%20out%20to%20tenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room%20of%20the%20home%20has%20a%20dinner%20table%2C%20a%20couch%2C%20and%20a%20television.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894c8d9cfc04e97619b0300%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20of%20the%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cole%20Flynn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGollisz%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Between%20November%202023%20and%20November%202024%2C%20a%20group%20of%20military-affiliated%20students%20rented%20the%20entire%20home%2C%20paying%20%242%2C100%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlynn%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20months%2C%20rent%20was%20about%20%24200%20short%2C%20so%20the%20three%20of%20us%20had%20to%20chip%20in%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20over%20the%20year.%20Operating%20at%20a%20slight%20loss%20has%20had%20its%20tax%20benefits%2C%20so%20it%20hasn't%20been%20a%20complete%20setback.%20Plus%2C%20we%20expect%20to%20see%20appreciation%20in%20the%20Tampa%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20interest%20rates%20come%20down%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D