n%20installing%20an%20entirely%20new%20air%20conditioning%20system%2C%20which%20cost%20about%20%247%2C000.%20We%20split%20the%20cost%20evenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223faf9de9-fb12-41af-a782-b69e11e5ff10%5C%22%3EWe%20want%20to%20keep%20investing%20in%20real%20estate%20as%20a%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlynn%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20think%20the%20goal%20for%20all%20of%20us%20going%20in%2C%20and%20it%20still%20remains%2C%20is%20for%20this%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecluttering-side-hustle-makes-money-preferred-over-corporate-job-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20side%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20help%20supplement%20our%20income%20and%20build%20up%20our%20net%20worth%20outside%20our%209-to-5%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20understood%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20long-term%20relationship%2C%20and%20there%20has%20to%20be%20constant%20communication.%20We%20all%20trust%20each%20other%20to%20put%20our%20heads%20down%20and%20do%20the%20work%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGollisz%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20do%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuying-home-with-friend-pros-cons-affordability-wills-legal-concerns-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eco-buying%20with%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Buying%20alone%20can%20be%20very%20daunting%2C%20especially%20when%20you're%20young%2C%20but%20it%20definitely%20feels%20less%20scary%20and%20more%20achievable%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20our%20friendship%20actually%20grew%20more%20by%20being%20business%20partners.%20Even%20though%20Scott%20moved%20down%20South%20and%20we%20don't%20see%20him%20as%20much%2C%20we%20keep%20in%20touch%20by%20talking%20about%20the%20property.%20And%20when%20he%20comes%20back%20to%20New%20York%20every%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20we%20get%20together%20and%20rehash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20very%20excited%20about%20the%20property's%20future.%20We're%20