a%20mattress%20toppers%20have%20similar%2C%20simple%20designs.%20The%20Linenspa%20and%20Lucid%20I%20tested%20are%20both%20three-inch%20slabs%20of%20cushy%2C%20compressive%20CertiPUR-US-certified%20memory%20foam%20(meaning%20it's%20free%20from%20toxic%20chemicals)%20that%20sit%20directly%20on%20top%20of%20your%20mattress.%20They%20don't%20have%20straps%20or%20skirted%20elastic%20to%20attach%20them%20to%20the%20mattress%2C%20but%20thankfully%2C%20they%20didn't%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lucid%20mattress%20topper%20is%20made%20of%20CertiPUR-US-certified%20memory%20foam%20infused%20with%20bamboo%20and%20charcoal.%20This%20gives%20the%20topper%20a%20soft%20gray%20color%20and%20helps%20wick%20away%20moisture%20and%20regulate%20odors.%20The%20topper%20also%20has%20air%20holes%20for%20additional%20ventilation.%20It's%20sold%20in%20two-inch%2C%20three-inch%2C%20and%20four-inch%20varieties.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20the%20taller%20toppers%20will%20be%20plusher%2C%20more%20contouring%2C%20and%20cause%20your%20body%20to%20sink%20the%20most%2C%20while%20the%20thinner%20toppers%20will%20have%20a%20firmer%2C%20more%20on-top%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Linenspa%20topper%20is%20also%20made%20with%20CertiPUR-US-certified%20foam%2C%20but%20it's%20infused%20with%20cooling%20gel.%20The%20cooling%20gel%20stands%20out%20as%20dark%20blue%20specks%20against%20the%20light%20blue%20topper.%20The%20Linenspa%20topper%20doesn't%20have%20ventilation%20holes.%20It's%20also%20available%20in%20a%20two-inch%20thickness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20brands%20offer%20the%20toppers%20with%20a%20removable%2C%20machine-washable%20cover%2C%20which%20I%20recommend%20since%20the%20foam%20itself%20is%20spot-clean%20only%2C%20but%20it%20does%20add%20to%20the%20cost.%20I%20also%20recommend%20protecting%20your%20mattress%20topper%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-protector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emattress%20protector%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20its%20lifespan%20in%20the%20event%20of%20sweat%20or%20spills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22410deaa0-13be-4c13-9184-db228e97eab4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucid%20vs%20Linenspa%3A%20Setup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20two%20mattress%20toppers%20wrapped%20in%20plastic%20after%20unboxing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689657a1cfc04e97619b240f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20the%20Lucid%20and%20Linenspa%20are%20simple%20sheets%20of%20memory%20foam%20to%20soften%20up%20a%20firm%20mattress.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20toppers%20arrive%20in%20a%20box%20about%20the%20size%20of%20an%20end%20table.%20Inside%2C%20the%20memory%20foam%20is%20compressed%20and%20rolled%20within%20a%20layer%20of%20tissue%20paper%20and%20plastic%20wrap.%20On%20first%20impression%2C%20these%20toppers%20feel%20very%20distinct%20from%20one%20another.%20After%20unboxing%2C%20the%20Lucid%20topper%20was%20significantly%20compressed%2C%20with%20a%20texture%20that%20reminded%20me%20(rather%20specifically)%20of%20crushed%20cotton%20candy.%20As%20such%2C%20it%20took%20much%20longer%20to%20expand%20than%20the%20Linenspa%20mattress%20topper%2C%20which%20popped%20out%20of%20the%20plastic%20basically%20ready%20to%20go%20%E2%80%94%20although%20the%20brand%20recommends%20letting%20it%20air%20out%20for%2024%20to%2048%20hours%20after%20opening.%20I%20attribute%20the%20different%20texture%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20toppers%3A%20Lucid%20is%20plusher%2C%20whereas%20the%20Linenspa%20has%20high-density%20foam%2C%20so%20it%20springs%20into%20place%20quickly.%20Both%20had%20a%20slight%20chemical%20scent%20that%20faded%20by%20bedtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cca9aada-3017-4e69-8977-83db9c007f66%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucid%20vs%20Linenspa%3A%20Comfort%20and%20support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20similar%20appearance%2C%20the%20Lucid%20and%20Linenspa%20mattress%20toppers%20are%20notably%20distinct%20in%20terms%20of%20comfort%20and%20support.%20Both%20are%20comfortable%20and%20supportive%20toppers%20that%20can%20soften%20a%20firm%20bed%2C%20but%20which%20is%20best%20for%20you%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20sleeping%20position%20and%20comfort%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20side%20sleepers%20looking%20for%20a%20super%20soft%2C%20cushy%20topper%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20Lucid.%20The%20Lucid%20topper%20isn't%20as%20firm%20as%20the%20Linenspa%2C%20and%20it%20adapts%20to%20the%20curves%20of%20your%20body%20to%20support%20pressure%20points%2C%20like%20the%20hips%2C%20while%20you%20sleep.%20This%20feel%20is%20perfect%20for%20side%20sleepers%2C%20since%20your%20body%20can%20sink%20into%20the%20mattress%2C%20keeping%20your%20spine%20aligned%20as%20you%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20might%20not%20enjoy%20the%20plushness%2C%20though.%20I'm%20a%20plus-size%20person%2C%20and%20I%20found%20myself%20sinking%20into%20the%20Lucid%20topper%20too%20much%20for%20my%20liking.%20At%20times%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20sea%20of%20memory%20foam%2C%20making%20moving%20around%20at%20night%20or%20getting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed%20difficult.%20The%20Lucid%20topper%20is%20better%20suited%20for%20people%20with%20lighter%20bodies%2C%20since%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20sinking%20in%20and%20can%20enjoy%20the%20plushness%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Linenspa%20topper%20is%20cushy%20yet%20firm.%20I%20never%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Bstuck%26quot%3B%20in%20bed%20when%20I%20used%20it%2C%20and%20I%20could%20move%20around%20easily.%20The%20topper%20still%20adapts%20to%20fit%20your%20body%2C%20but%20the%20feeling%20is%20much%20subtler%20than%20the%20Lucid%20mattress%20topper.%20I%20recommend%20the%20Linenspa%20for%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers%2C%20who%20usually%20require%20a%20firmer%20surface%20than%20side%20sleepers.%20Don't%20worry%2C%20though%3A%20it's%20not%20overwhelmingly%20firm%2C%20so%20it%20will%20still%20soften%20up%20any%20uncomfortable%20mattress.%20It's%20also%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20heavy%20people%2C%20since%20you%20won't%20sink%20into%20this%20topper%20as%20much%20as%20the%20Lucid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20preferred%20the%20pressure%20relief%20of%20the%20Linenspa%20topper%2C%20but%20side%20sleepers%20might%20prefer%20the%20Lucid.%20It%20just%20depends%20whether%20you%20prefer%20the%20foam%20to%20fully%20engulf%20your%20pressure%20points%20or%20offer%20gentler%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245af963f-418f-4fdd-8d9c-563ad8402569%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucid%20vs%20Linenspa%3A%20Cooling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Lucid%20and%20Linenspa%20mattress%20toppers%20have%20features%20to%20keep%20hot%20sleepers%20cool%20and%20sweat-free%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20making%20them%20viable%20options%20to%20consider%20if%20you%20require%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-mattress-topper-for-hot-sleepers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20cooling%20mattress%20topper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20the%20way%20they%20do%20so%20is%20a%20bit%20different.%20Lucid%20infuses%20its%20memory%20foam%20with%20bamboo%20and%20charcoal%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20also%20help%20absorb%20odors%20and%20is%20ventilated%20for%20airflow%2C%20while%20Linenspa's%20cooling%20gel%20foam%20helps%20regulate%20body%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20Lucid%20had%20better%20heat%20dissipation%20(meaning%20it%20wicks%20heat%20away%20faster)%2C%20while%20the%20Linenspa%20stayed%20cooler%20for%20longer.%20To%20test%20cooling%2C%20I%20measured%20the%20topper's%20temperature%20before%20going%20to%20bed%2C%20immediately%20after%20waking%20up%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20out%20of%20bed.%20On%20average%2C%20the%20Lucid%20topper%20had%20a%20starting%20temperature%20of%2074.6%20degrees%2C%20while%20the%20Linenspa%20measured%20in%20at%2071.8%20degrees%2C%20in%20a%20room%20with%20the%20same%20ambient%20temperature.%20Both%20toppers%20increased%20about%2010%20degrees%20immediately%20after%20waking%20up%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20Linenspa%20stayed%20the%20coolest%20at%20night.%20After%20the%20two-minute%20period%2C%20the%20Linenspa%20only%20dropped%20two%20degrees%2C%20while%20the%20Lucid%20dropped%20over%20seven%20degrees%2C%20showing%20incredible%20results%20for%20heat%20dissipation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d555f686-cbf9-451c-aea9-571d3209f611%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucid%20vs%20Linenspa%3A%20Motion%20isolation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMotion%20isolation%20refers%20to%20the%20way%20movement%20is%20transferred%20through%20a%20mattress.%20Motion%20isolation%20is%20important%20for%20couples%20or%20people%20who%20share%20a%20bed%20with%20pets%2C%20so%20your%20sleep%20isn't%20interrupted%20by%20twitching%20legs%20or%20midnight%20zoomies.%20To%20test%20motion%20isolation%2C%20I%20placed%20a%20soda%20can%20near%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20bed.%20Then%2C%20I%20dropped%20a%2015-pound%20weight%20a%20foot%20away%20from%20the%20can%2010%20times%20while%20observing%20if%20the%20can%20shifted%2C%20tipped%2C%20or%20fell%20over%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20mattress%20toppers%20had%20comparable%20motion%20isolation%2C%20with%20the%20Lucid%20narrowly%20edging%20out%20the%20Linenspa%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20minimize%20motion%20transfer.%20The%20can%20tipped%20over%20twice%20in%20my%20Lucid%20test%2C%20whereas%20it%20tipped%20over%20three%20times%20on%20the%20Linenspa.%20This%20is%20probably%20because%20the%20Lucid%20topper%20uses%20softer%20foam%2C%20so%20motion%20is%20easily%20absorbed%20into%20the%20material.%20Subjectively%2C%20I%20never%20felt%20movements%20from%20my%20dog%20or%20boyfriend%20when%20testing%20either%20topper.%20Both%20toppers%20are%20a%20solid%20choice%20for%20couples%20and%20people%20with%20pets%2C%20though%20you%20might%20feel%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20movement%20across%20the%20bed%20if%20your%20sleeping%20companions%20are%20particularly%20restless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f21525e-5233-461e-acb1-c865a4af6aa0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucid%20vs%20Linenspa%3A%20Trial%20and%20warranty%20policies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lucid%20and%20Linenspa%20mattress%20toppers%20can%20be%20returned%20within%2030%20days%20of%20purchase%20and%20come%20with%20a%203-year%20limited%20warranty.%20Lucid's%20warranty%20covers%20manufacturing%20defects%20but%20doesn't%20apply%20to%20general%20wear%20and%20tear%2C%20indentations%20less%20than%201.5%20inches%20deep%2C%20stains%2C%20misuse%2C%20third-party%20repair%2C%20damage%20from%20transit%2C%20or%20commercial%20use.%20Linenspa's%20warranty%20covers%20the%20same%20things%2C%20but%20excludes%20coverage%20of%20indentations%20less%20than%200.75%20inches%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20successfully%20claim%20your%20warranty%2C%20Lucid%20and%20Linenspa%20will%20issue%20a%20repair%2C%20replacement%2C%20or%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22847ce486-5736-4a6c-9d08-8af94d3af89c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20two%20mattress%20toppers%20on%20a%20mattress%20side%20by%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689659aef748d8c055f731a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20its%20support%20and%20subtle%20feel%2C%20the%20Linenspa%20was%20the%20victor%20in%20the%20Lucid%20vs%20Linenspa%20match.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lucid%20Bamboo%20Charcoal%20Mattress%20Topper%20and%20the%20Linenspa%20Memory%20Foam%20Mattress%20Topper%20are%20both%20excellent%2C%20supportive%20budget%20options%20that%20excel%20in%20cooling%20and%20have%20good%20motion%20isolation.%20I%20recommend%20side%20sleepers%20and%20those%20who%20want%20to%20sink%20into%20the%20foam%20to%20go%20with%20the%20Lucid%2C%20while%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers%20will%20appreciate%20the%20more%20balanced%20feel%20of%20the%20Linenspa%20topper.%20If%20you're%20stuck%20between%20the%20two%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20Linenspa%3A%20it's%20best%20for%20most%20people%20and%20will%20cost%20about%20%2410%20less%20than%20the%20Lucid.%20Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flinenspa-gel-infused-memory-foam-mattress-topper-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinenspa%20gel-infused%20mattress%20topper%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flucid-vs-linenspa-mattress-topper%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754935261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68965a20194a2d49b8ae4b7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flucid-vs-linenspa-mattress-topper%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20took%20two%20popular%20budget%20memory%20foam%20mattress%20toppers%20from%20Lucid%20and%20Linenspa%20head-to-head%2C%20comparing%20the%20design%2C%20comfort%2C%20support%20and%20cooling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kinsley%20Searles)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flucid-vs-linenspa-mattress-topper%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Income-Tax%20Bill%20restores%20alternate%20minimum%20tax%20relief%20for%20LLPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754934686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-08