tood%20a%20wild%20tiger%20staring%20right%20at%20me.%20Then%20for%20the%20next%2015%20minutes%2C%20both%20the%20tiger%20and%20I%20were%20imitating%20each%20other.%20When%20I%20sat%20down%20quietly%2C%20he%20also%20sat.%20When%20I%20got%20up%2C%20he%20also%20moved%20back.%20Then%20suddenly%2C%20when%20I%20made%20a%20loud%20noise%2C%20the%20tiger%20ran%20away.%20The%20next%20day%20when%20I%20came%20back%20to%20the%20same%20spot%2C%20I%20found%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20Sambar%20Deer%20lying%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20had%20encountered%20a%20hungry%20tiger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeopards%2C%20bears%2C%20tigers%2C%20stray%20wolves%2C%20snakes%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20long%20list%20of%20animals%20that%20Maari%20has%20encountered.%20But%20rather%20than%20being%20scared%2C%20this%20man%20has%20embraced%20these%20experiences%20that%20have%20brought%20him%20closer%20to%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESilent%20Valley%20Today%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFeatured-Image-1-2020-04-01T123007.221.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFeatured-Image-1-2020-04-01T123007.221.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFeatured-Image-1-2020-04-01T123007.221-300x157.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFeatured-Image-1-2020-04-01T123007.221-500x262.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFeatured-Image-1-2020-04-01T123007.221-768x402.png%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-222602%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3