20Rs%20150%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202%2C500%20kilos%20of%20papaya%20are%20supplied%20daily%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20market%20from%20Hooghly%20district.%20Two%20trucks%2C%20each%20carrying%201%2C250%20kilos%2C%20make%20the%20daily%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CEIC%20Data%E2%80%99s%20mid-2025%20report%2C%20West%20Bengal%20produced%20334.161%20tonnes%20of%20papaya.%20India%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20papaya%20producer%2C%20accounting%20for%2044%20percent%20of%20the%20global%20output%20at%2053%20lakh%20tonnes%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanting%2C%20care%20and%20cultivation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPapaya%20plants%20are%20fragile%20and%20need%20bamboo%20supports.%20Halder%20maintains%20a%206%20to%208-foot%20gap%20between%20each%20plant%20and%20finds%20clay%20soil%20optimal.%20Male%20plants%20flower%3B%20females%20bear%20fruit.%20Plants%20usually%20survive%20for%20two%20years%20and%20are%20then%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20invest%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20bigha%20for%20fresh%20cultivation.%20Although%20farmers%20get%20tax%20exemptions%2C%20we%20still%20have%20to%20pay%20land%20revenue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalder%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F471529%2Fgrowing-organic-shiitake-mushrooms-nagaland-lhuvevolu-rhakho%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20nurtures%20each%20plant%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20mustard%20flakes%2C%20groundnut%20flakes%2C%20and%20urea.%20Pesticides%20like%20Merivon%20and%20Rogor%20keep%20insects%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-9_11zon-1754545373.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20papaya%20variety%20by%20Bengal%